file.name: swagger-api_mobile.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Swagger Cloudtrust Management
  description: 'API Mobile self service for Cloudtrust'
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
- url: http://localhost:8844
paths:
  /mobile/userinfo:
    get:
      tags:
      - UserInfo
      summary: Gets information of the current user
      responses:
        200:
          description: successful operation
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/UserInfo'
components:
  schemas:
    UserInfo:
      type: object
      properties:
        realmDisplayName:
          type: string
          description: display name of the realm
        accreditations:
          type: array
          items:
            type: object
            properties:
              type:
                type: string
                description: accreditation type
              expiryDate:
                type: string
                description: expiry date. format is DD.MM.YYYY
              expired:
                type: boolean
                description: true if the expiry date has passed
              revoked:
                type: boolean
                description: true if the accreditation has been revoked
        checks:
          type: array
          items:
            type: object
            properties:
              type:
                type: string
                description: type
              nature:
                type: string
                description: nature
              date:
                type: string
                description: check date. format is DD.MM.YYYY
        actions:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
            description: actions supposed to be shown as enabled
        pendingActions:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
            description: actions supposed to be shown as disabled
  securitySchemes:
    openId:
      type: openIdConnect
      openIdConnectUrl: http://toto.com/.well-known/openid-configuration
security:
  - openId:
    - todo
